OSPF features:
Open shortest path first
It is an IGP - Interior gateway protocol and it is used to route the info
within the autonotmous system
It uses the multicast address 224.0.0.5 and .6
cost can be calculated 10power of 8
Classless routing protocol supports VLSM and CIDR
send hello packets in reg intervals
router id plays an important role 
three types of ospf table
Neighbour table: contains list of directly connected routers cmd: show ip ospf neighbour
topology table: contanis list of all possible route inside the area
it is also knon as LSDB link state Database CMD : Show ip ospf database
Routing Table: list of best path to each destination CMd: show ip route